metadata.package-name: Dutch spelling dictionary for use with MarkLogic Server
metadata.description: This dictionary is based on the GNU Aspell Dutch Word List Package by Kevin Atkinson, based on a word list by multiple authors. See "sources" below for details. Greg Murray added XML tags to the word list to conform to the MarkLogic schema for spelling dictionaries.
